OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and sunny start in
OL,6,FInverness and the east, with a touch
OL,7,Fof frost in places, but cloudier with
OL,8,Fshowers in west. The showers will
OL,9,Fspread east to all areas during the
OL,10,Fmorning with bright intervals in
OL,11,Fbetween.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBright spells and a few
OL,14,Fshowers during the evening. A band of
OL,15,Fcloud and outbreaks of rain will then
OL,16,Fmove south overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
