OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloud and outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fwill clear from the south early
OL,7,Fmorning. Otherwise a bright day with
OL,8,Fsunny spells and scattered showers,
OL,9,Fthese wintry on the mountains. Feeling
OL,10,Fcool.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,13,Ftouch of frost early Wednesday then
OL,14,Fmainly dry and bright, but showers
OL,15,Farriving later. Rain or showers
OL,16,FThursday and Friday. Feeling rather
OL,17,Fcool for the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
